What's this?
------------

The @PACKAGE_NAME@ package contains Linux FireWire utilities for
listing devices (lsfirewire, lsfirewirephy) and for querying and
configuring devices (firewire-request).


Installation
------------

This package uses GNU Autoconf; you can use the standard installation
sequence::

  configure
  make
  make install


